./runtime/logs/task-point-state-machine-resolution-discuss-point-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:108:- S-001: Single-tier precedence where the explicit invocation override is the highest-priority complete state-machine selection, followed by rhei-local `**States:**`, inherited `index.panta.md` project default, and built-in `rhei` fallback.
