./runtime/logs/task-point-state-machine-resolution-aggregate-disagreements-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:226:+  - Why it matters: This determines whether operators can temporarily change the effective state machine for a run, or can only redirect to another YAML file implementing the already-declared machine name. It also changes which mistakes validation can catch when an override is present.
